            . </span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Pulse duration (ms) </td><td>2.5±0.4 </td><td>3.5±0.3 </td></tr><tr><td>Pulse interval (ms) </td><td>72.3±23.4 </td><td>80.7±18.9 </td></tr><tr><td>Minimum frequency of fundamental harmonic (kHz) </td><td>18.6±0.8 </td><td>19.3±0.8 </td></tr><tr><td>Frequency of most energy in fundamental harmonic (kHz) </td><td>27.7±2.7 </td><td>26.6±1.4 </td></tr><tr><td>Maximum frequency of fundamental harmonic (kHz) </td><td>37.4±2.1 </td><td>36.3±1.5 </td></tr><tr><td>Upper frequency of third harmonic (kHz) </td><td>90.7±4.9 </td><td>86.3±2.9 </td></tr><tr><td>Frequency of most energy in second harmonic (kHz) </td><td>49.3±2.5 </td><td>45.5±1.7 </td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="table-wrap-foot"><div class="fn" content-id=""><p>Calls were recorded in a forested area close to the roost or from three bats released in an open area devoid of trees. Means ± S.D. of all calls are reported.</p></div></div><div class="graphic-wrap hide"><a class="fig-view-orig openInAnotherWindow btn js-view-large" href="/view-large/7565334" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">View Large</a></div></div>
